753
00:38:00,287 --> 00:38:01,087
Pendekar Mu.

754
00:38:02,647 --> 00:38:04,607
Pertimbangkan lagi dengan baik.

755
00:38:06,167 --> 00:38:07,328
Aku pamit dulu.

756
00:38:29,167 --> 00:38:30,008
Pangeran.

757
00:39:20,096 --> 00:39:23,264
♪Berkelana di penjuru dunia persilatan♪

758
