767
00:39:53,088 --> 00:39:55,872
♪Seluruh dendam telah terputus♪

768
00:39:55,872 --> 00:39:59,104
♪Hanya tersisa saling membunuh
dan perselisihan♪

769
00:39:59,360 --> 00:40:02,016
♪Jangan takut, jangan panik♪

770
00:40:02,208 --> 00:40:05,440
♪Satu dunia persilatan,
